title: Workflow Execution State UDRs - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: The Workflow Bridge forwarding agent sends information to the Workflow Bridge real-time collection agent to report workflow state changes. The state information is delivered in a WorkflowStateUDR .
